        <h2 id="what-is">What is an AI SEO agent?</h2>
        <p>An AI SEO agent is software that <strong>executes SEO tasks autonomously</strong>. Not "suggests." Not "drafts." Executes — and reports back. The agent category covers four big jobs:</p>
